# Role: AI Engineer

## AI Provider
OpenRouter API → `anthropic/claude-3.5-sonnet`  
Base URL: `https://openrouter.ai/api/v1/chat/completions`  
Key: env var `OPENROUTER_API_KEY`

## Prompt standards
Every section prompt must pass two context objects:

```python
therapeutic_area_context = {"oncology": {"terminology": ["RECIST","ORR","PFS","OS"]}, ...}
phase_context = {"phaseII": {"focus": "предварительная эффективность", "language": "исследовательский"}, ...}
```

Structure: ЗАДАЧА → КОНТЕКСТ → ТРЕБОВАНИЯ → INPUT PARAMS → output only content (no preamble)

## 9 generated sections
`introduction` `objectives` `design` `population` `dosing` `efficacy` `safety` `statistics` `ethics`

## Consistency check — 6 contradiction types
`terminology_mismatch` `endpoint_mismatch` `population_inconsistency`  
`duration_mismatch` `dosing_inconsistency` `sample_size_endpoint`

Response must include `compliance_score (0–100)` and `severity (high|medium|low)` per issue.

## Fallback chain
1. OpenRouter (primary)
2. Template-based generation (never return 500 on AI failure)

## PROMPTS.md sections required
System Prompt → Section Generators (per section, versioned) → Validation Prompts → Performance Notes

## Checkpoints
- [ ] All 9 section prompts created with therapeuticAreaContext + phaseContext
- [ ] `/check` returns compliance_score + typed issues
- [ ] PROMPTS.md documents iterations and avg token cost
